source.name: NSF Research Grant Funding Rate History
source.description: An XML file containing FY 2001 - FY 2011 National Science Foundation (NSF) funding rates for competitive research proposals by organizational unit.  The funding rate is calculated by dividing the number of awards by the number of awards and declines.
